> ![http://i52.tinypic.com/2ptxmz9.png](http://i52.tinypic.com/2ptxmz9.png "http://i52.tinypic.com/2ptxmz9.png")

**Here is a new bomb/defuse map. Just to tell you a bit about it, it has 32 player spawns and 2 bomb targets. It looks like a factory in the desert with all the attachments. A crane (drops a car with a button), water towers, smoke tower, loads of tanks and a working helicopter with sound. There are underground tunnels and ladders for getting on high ground.**

**This is the first version, so please do comment for any bugs mistakes as I will make version 2 if needed. If this will become a popular map, witch I hope it will, I can create a night sky version.**

**About the sounds part: the looping sounds are the sound of the helicopter of course (not too loud, so it's not annoying) and also the main looping sound is the war & battle firing. Minor sounds included are some steam sounds, pipes, machines...**

**The map has effects like: fire, smoke, steam, etc.**

**That concludes the description :) Hope you comment, rate, and report for any bugs. (please don't flag, rather comment and I will fix it)** 

> **To install, simply put the cstrike folder in the download over your old one and overwrite.**

**Hope you like the map and ENJOY! :D**
